Miro comes with a set of config files for the various robots.

The configuration files are located in the directory etc. Sample
configurations are available for the supported platforms. They are
named <platform>.xml.

To get a cofiguration file for your robot just copy or link the
according configuration file to a file named after the robots name:

cp <platform>.xml $HOST.xml

or 

ln -s <platform>.xml $HOST.xml
